{{Quote|Do not let night find you in the Well of the Dead. The katarn still owns the shadows and the darkness, and even the Wookiees must respect that.|[[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]]|<ref name="Tyrant's Test">''[[Tyrant's Test]]''</ref>}}
The '''Well of the Dead''' was located on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] in the [[Shadowlands/Legends|Shadowlands]]. It was connected to [[Rwookrrorro/Legends|Rwookrrorro]] by the [[Rryatt Trail]]. Young [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] would go there to harvest [[Syren plant/Legends|syren plants]] or hunt [[Katarn/Legends|katarns]] for their initiation rites.

